imdb.plot outline: Karageade is a girl who has lots of problems in her life. When she was drunk she unconsciously sign a contract with seven other girls in the Cupid Hut that she will find a boyfriend in one year. Daniel is a half-caste guy who she meet and decide to go after him. Unknown to her Daniel is an undercover cop who is on the job investigate in a case. What will happened when they find out each other problems.
